01:35:35.347 --> 01:35:39.351
<i>Like a miniature paradise</i>

01:36:16.013 --> 01:36:20.559
<i>I go crazy sometimes</i>

01:36:20.976 --> 01:36:24.187
<i>Can you believe it?</i>

01:36:25.814 --> 01:36:28.675
<i>Yeah, I swear I'm fine</i>

01:36:28.775 --> 01:36:33.613
<i>That I'm all right
but I'm barely breathing</i>

01:36:34.990 --> 01:36:39.035
<i>Thought I could find my way back home</i>

01:36:39.536 --> 01:36:42.998
<i>But I get lost alone</i>

01:36:43.623 --> 01:36:45.834
<i>But when I'm with you</i>

01:36:45.959 --> 01:36:48.111
<i>I'm no longer wandering</i>

01:36:48.211 --> 01:36:52.716
<i>And when I'm with you
I swear I can breathe</i>

01:36:52.841 --> 01:36:54.743
<i>And when I'm with you</i>

01:36:54.843 --> 01:36:59.973
<i>I know who I am and who I want to be</i>

01:37:06.104 --> 01:37:09.900
<i>I'm not trying to be dramatic, no</i>

01:37:10.400 --> 01:37:14.029
<i>Most times I'm pretty normal</i>

01:37:16.031 --> 01:37:20.243
<i>Oh, let's be clear and honest here</i>

01:37:20.368 --> 01:37:24.247
<i>And do away with anything formal</i>

01:37:25.165 --> 01:37:29.444
<i>I can fake it on my own</i>

01:37:29.544 --> 01:37:33.465
